0 0 4 2 6 0
The edges of Minimum Cost Spanning Tree are
1 edge (1,3) =1
2 edge (4,6) =2
3 edge (1,2) =3
4 edge (2,5) =3
5 edge (3,6) =4

        Minimum cost = 13
	return 0;
}
Time complexity:O(E log V)
